3. comment to read_nc.py : before running the code save a version of bit.sea/instruments/matchup_manager.py

    with a changed line 215
    instead of ref_varname = self.reference_var(p, model_varname)
    put ref_varname = 'IRR_380'
    link this script to that version of bit.sea through PYTHONPATH=...
    

4. export PYTHONPATH=/galileo/home/userexternal/eterzic0/bit.sea
   export MASKFILE=/galileo/home/userexternal/eterzic0/CODE/ogstm/preproc/RADIATIVE_INWATER/meshmask.nc

5. run the profiler.py (change the path of VardescriptorB.xml accordingly)

